{
  "title": "about.md",
  "content": [
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "H1",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "Web Development Is A Scam"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Divider",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "Are we really gonna pay for this ancient (and garbage) tech service forever?"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "Websites are ancient tech."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "Stop being a part of the problem."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "H2",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "The Problem We're Solving"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "The website industry has made it such that people need a lot of knowledge, skill, and effort to get a website running, or be willing to pay a megacorp money to have the same hyper-consumerist flashbang of stock images of people smiling miserably and data-farming popups."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "Combine this with the diabolical trap that is the ease-of-setup and absolute technical nightmare that one of those websites become once you start doing stuff with it..."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "H2",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "Our Solution"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "People need to write out the stuff they need to write in order to have anything to put on the website, right?"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "So, if someone were to "
          }
        },
        {
          "Bold": {
            "String": "actually care"
          }
        },
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": " about the "
          }
        },
        {
          "Bold": {
            "String": "user"
          }
        },
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": " and nobody else... "
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "How would they go about making it as simple as possible to take that writing and transform it into a website?"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "We take that writing, as it is, ask that it be written in MarkDown (or our ExtendedMarkDown which is MD with stuff for a website that MD doesn't have), and turn it straight into a website. The pages and navigation is all handled programmatically crawling to see how the writing is set up in the directory that is its indicated root."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "In English: We turn that writing straight into a fully functional, nested navigation (if they want) website."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    }
  ]
}